snippet.title: Piper Gets In A Scrappy Fight w/ Jonah In An RV | Drive Angry
snippet.description:
Piper (Amber Heard) gets in a scrappy fight with Jonah (Billy Burke) in an RV as John (Nicolas Cage) tails behind them in the car.
